<%- include("partials/header") %>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-copy">
    <p class="eyebrow">Hosting Client Portal</p>
    <h1>遊戲伺服器與 Discord Bot 主機租用</h1>
    <p class="lead">選擇產品、調整方案、加入購物車，再用 ECPay 完成付款。系統會把帳戶與訂單集中到會員中心，並可同步 Pterodactyl Panel。</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="button primary" href="#plans">瀏覽產品</a>
      <a class="button ghost" href="/cart">查看購物車</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <aside class="client-card">
    <div class="client-card-head">
      <span class="status-dot"></span>
      <strong>產品分類</strong>
    </div>
    <a href="/products/<%= encodeURIComponent('Minecraft伺服器') %>">Minecraft伺服器</a>
    <a href="/products/<%= encodeURIComponent('Discord Bot') %>">Discord Bot</a>
    <a href="/cart">購物車與優惠代碼</a>
    <a href="/checkout">前往結帳</a>
  </aside>
</section>

<section class="quick-actions">
  <a href="/products/<%= encodeURIComponent('Minecraft伺服器') %>"><strong>Minecraft伺服器</strong><span>生存、模組、社群伺服器</span></a>
  <a href="/products/<%= encodeURIComponent('Discord Bot') %>"><strong>Discord Bot</strong><span>Node.js、Python、工具服務</span></a>
  <a href="/cart"><strong>優惠代碼</strong><span>在購物車或結帳套用折扣</span></a>
  <a href="/account"><strong>會員中心</strong><span>查看訂單與服務狀態</span></a>
</section>

<section id="plans" class="section">
  <div class="section-head">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Products</p>
      <h2>選擇方案</h2>
    </div>
    <p>點擊立即租用後會先進入產品詳細購買畫面，確認規格與數量後再加入購物車。</p>
  </div>
  <div class="plans">
    <% products.forEach((product) => { const specs = JSON.parse(product.specs); %>
      <article class="plan-card">
        <div class="plan-top">
          <span><%= product.category %></span>
          <h3><%= product.name %></h3>
          <p><%= product.description %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="price">NT$ <strong><%= product.price %></strong><small>/月</small></div>
        <ul class="specs">
          <% Object.entries(specs).forEach(([key, value]) => { %>
            <li><span><%= key %></span><strong><%= value %></strong></li>
          <% }) %>
        </ul>
        <a class="button primary full" href="/product/<%= product.id %>">立即租用</a>
      </article>
    <% }) %>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="automation" class="feature-band">
  <div>
    <p class="eyebrow">Automation</p>
    <h2>從購物車到控制台開通</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="features">
    <div><strong>產品設定</strong><span>先確認規格、數量與月租價格，再加入購物車。</span></div>
    <div><strong>優惠代碼</strong><span>支援百分比與固定金額折抵，結帳前清楚顯示。</span></div>
    <div><strong>ECPay 金流</strong><span>付款完成後回寫訂單並嘗試開通服務。</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="support" class="section compact">
  <h2>客戶支援</h2>
  <p>如需調整方案、優惠代碼或開通狀態，可從會員中心查看訂單並聯繫支援。</p>
</section>

<%- include("partials/footer") %>
